info.name: Wikipedia 1911 (Dark) (Fixed)
info.description:
This is a fork of a fork of the great Wikipedia 1911. This one covers even more obscure elements. I promise to update this regularly.

Complementary styles:
Wikipedia 1911 - force dark table data - Forces dark table cells for cells with style embedded in HTML.
Wikipedia - invert formulas for nightmode styles - Makes some images dark.
